# ScratchBird-ai

AI integration project for ScratchBird.

## Repository Layout

- `docs/reference/` - research inputs and external/tooling references
- `docs/specifications/` - implementation specifications derived from reference material
- `src/` - implementation code (tool servers, adapters, orchestration)
- `tests/` - automated tests and evaluation harnesses
- `examples/` - runnable integration examples
- `tools/` - local developer scripts

## Documentation Workflow

1. Capture and curate inputs in `docs/reference/`.
2. Produce concrete implementation specs in `docs/specifications/drafts/`.
3. Promote approved specs to `docs/specifications/final/`.
4. Implement in `src/` and validate in `tests/`.
